t-size: 16px;"&gt;。&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;对于韩国总统李在明来说，伊朗战争既带来了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/GL8M-MeP6TLBDdt9wtNmsCTCmYPyCHBMb7YvCKmT6Se5TnOU5wx-EFWK_cOU-U7KPDXTtl-CwLnJRaoPWQCXB6LuAf-JJm0TGwgeN8ZIa3iWRfs1Ja5hHMxMIStKTyRb_n_lYj0pyodTIL-O7u7aN8ldFqH2jwceadn7AKvBWbR0bqwXK2DeTnsYz11OuBGUYFJA-_FkMZpOCavfPhBFg9rcdp7TGXUkVyEl3R1NQP1MuPYMtVj-cnMJORhhyq8Wbhzpf0g_EsvDagwBNQKR18gX83JHWqQwblRQGj0fO03YIhYUwYmsQarUOdvILmv3-I-9Y5R0_vUgmsLsuu4mp6pp1-KC76L1hb32rg5LclUJdJxsiwEfhr7zCYwxIk1uojj8TLr-HLMoKIXYTyRRn2FPgt4mYpGD78uyNlGRFzvcSLKKC0drmkae96LjNQgrj7EWvDIAdeZlMPVhD2054eX1hHFFW5H74pjImBw9z23awN4aHo3sLYQclvmosuwNwpvW-kU__qmY9OfCD5Tz/c6mdFitO17Nfj_p33TKFip5RW_8PFF-R/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普的霍尔木兹封锁有可能加剧整个亚洲的痛苦"&gt;前所未有的能源危机&lt;/a&gt;，也带来了加强首尔对抗&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/h7HdbcMfrnXBdtQXwg2F8hibslOwYccP05npBx9VWmWnDCP3HY8fwzAfK3RkSr56dn-85iQFrzcRMBwPNYVxfPmR1Mio4DWVXxte_WPd-MMVnCk7VgqDuY-mMiR1cdEIamjUFAlIAKq62XcpLcaRvyozqkPUwa5T8UyLrBhaQv_FakHSxMGcgrUAQ0VMRq2-vy9PjfWrsvds7RwsmTAyEA_fv05Ewjti6RzH5boK76uX9oCX6WEmstsMqv3sQPfNvArgptW6uuRvtrkLrKuBx9th4C1rPOEmeU-FVew8OumMoPCbOKYaDo7railqSEJ2RZH3S6Kp--S5k-dAuNGV4qSHiPT_jd6B-4IBolbD5-CusUz-c_KPt2LbttcgZ8svIJppuuog-I4aT3_Lj3Wi373hBODeBjBS0Y0PotquMQJiQZas3AaDGEQrsgKW1ho69d3N_-BlMxD2rKkWw5481gH3Q2Tx2uh68npOwkV5N-eKVN70ejjDCwMDbhciCfdSCnt0jei8HueJJyzm5draAg/Mos91jxSjKarrR4U84fNLUXri6YdmnMR/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="金正恩在特朗普中国之行前炫耀朋友和武器"&gt;朝鲜金正恩的&lt;/a&gt;新机会。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;就在上个月，韩国财政部长具润哲还吹嘘中东国家正在“排队”购买韩国导弹，并宣称成功率约为 90%。他们更&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/3-X2ebMliwlNpwLdcV166OIM7Z-Bkh2e61_i2lAXt6PL4qLZJnzG_jINfdQrxYDxMpyQVfxL3tZpp69mCt8nGpx5smH7YMmw7tf1dxqY7m4KXQ7_Mh4DtH1Z-R7T6LJsbgCNvL5fmmjMKOTtbbQeK2OX3_0Kmt7TBljfTp72d8FlJxjCnv3sYpiH5hgHiqWpgZqOOToiK0VuefyPrF-GzHWFjeMm6wRbUVp_EykBT0ui7QOxB-tbRd8lxbVEPokrGP6vYlEbb-YkrTCl31-SjgekCiP23xH51f3gYaKx4BzHJAIWPgIXj6Sl6UiLsexPmrA266sHFaHm5OpXDC7c0TZhuIHindoBDt8Tj9ID-NJ0UVM3wxcSRfQjKPcfsv65PMOzGwirupLiZe0TDqB6ZoqU7KG3T21mZKIHgCEjeB4BRQuwsKHv8gk40ONrXKkxMlwsOF2KRoFoCTWye5ML8TFQKtCMxqn9zXr0-FkwAiE7GaOs3_hc9_NCrA8LQNcnmRCv-D9tPIYyvmNO14cSLA/M3JCb-IhvxXx0yQkGcKlOA25Jw-DZsve/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="韩国拦截导弹即将下架"&gt;实惠的&lt;/a&gt;价格标签是另一个卖点。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;此后，首尔的部长们一直对确切的订单讳莫如深，而且尚不清楚韩华航空航天公司和其他军火制造商能否满足需求。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQpz5qAnbv.M/v10/-1x-1.jpg" alt="South Korean Navy&amp;amp;#39;s SSM-700K Haesung Anti-ship missile, front, and Haeryong ship-launched land attack missile displayed during a military parade in Seoul, South Korea, on Tuesday, Sept. 26, 2023. South Korea held its first military parade in a decade in Seoul that features thousands of troops and its latest military hardware to celebrate Armed Forces Day, just as it bolsters security ties with the US and Japan. Photographer: SeongJoon Cho&amp;amp;#x2F;Bloomberg" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="2023 年 9 月 26 日星期二，韩国海军在首尔举行的阅兵式上展示了 SSM-700K 海星反舰导弹、正面导弹和海龙舰载对地攻击导弹。韩国在首尔举行了十年来的首次阅兵，派出数千名士兵并配备了最新的军事装备来庆祝建军节，同时加强与美国和日本的安全关系。摄影师：SeongJoon Cho&amp;amp;#x2F;Bloomberg" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQpz5qAnbv.M/v10/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;"&gt; 2023 年 9 月在首尔举行的阅兵式。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;摄影师：SeongJoon Cho/彭博社&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;相反，政府的公众关注点是石油紧缩，李甚至要求公民通过缩短淋浴时间来节约能源。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;本周，一名韩国高级官员从哈萨克斯坦、阿曼和沙特阿拉伯归来，获得了数百万桶原油和新鲜石脑油供应，这些原油和新鲜石脑油供应将通过避开霍尔木兹海峡的航线运送，这让人松了口气。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;承诺公布时并未提及导弹，但首尔生产海湾国家和其他地区国家所需的武器也无伤大雅。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;波兰去年签署了一项价值 65 亿美元的购买&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/1_PSVIV2UPtE004BlcxfeJZenPIgYCqyjTBZsVgAbMsT8peAwG78LTe6cNvaoqF5u0nH-rPulVp5_ClV-KitSlmF_ENbyiUWzwadeEfqpkkkL9RvOK2Z-YzITizBfG_ivYMvEDAmAm4u4dHA7qcfflQUZmvOIXt1sl5MgvEvFr2Z_zO5wpKMsyllIxDvXaZHbvY4sShT9QmiBpnHIwMPXuwm9mDSHlptcnOPFhzZMUXSKbs8UYloc7Jm4J6jzmbN90hIPk-RsGgYj1Cuy6mx20doP_PaKReJT1KX9Q9J90jVMgGUMjlM9gqfCda8u05xteAIN06DFUF3yOoa6Hd8nk3TRGBlEBH6x9jGmW52NQmLK9X0Q6TNXNtX9LtgPCxdyBzZ-c7SSwSYEZtPWefnKFgFiiuV7vz4_YcRg20PILIEvhgtH3_8er23X5VPVSOElFzw8fiDMWykgrFrSXO98vnf5Cx7FCAs72CJxYfNbV6ICrTD-2fspcW3ZE_3XaNDqtYqESzK2np0Mt1LRdQTHcwt_d7dfXzdVMnUVA/1RemoFZFjD347rUEqLvqPpIqYGk4ulIE/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="波兰将国防预算增加了一倍。大部分现金流向国外"&gt;K-2 主战坦克的&lt;/a&gt;协议，就在本周，李和总理唐纳德·图斯克同意&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/ZkS9qpldNX3dWx-Eo-WtkC9RpofLuBVgERT2-ncmEJOt0FSLNuhfggBfoImJyYZJ8076D0M7E68g9NOIJN2KC5dnulUzk1ogrC1VszN594pFfRTrX-EGOpHrNjFT5R0OmdPKCEd6AJJ8QDkH9REJmYU3awckRuYr7RPU0XPkAwkimAQ8Fc38QXoCTQdtYKupzMQ9YEpfbe0XMHILWvMxgNObsomxaeBrb3Bp2gWwWaie0BHy4GmOBs5g71UWmaKLPpr2VNz27dIuwbyFhD5KAiN4wwZCkLtQiL43rLC96EqNQVhFFFzSHfjxrBW47VHvO7pBimdOIqVf7nsdWebGev2-_oEW2abwAOVvKl1ccW-BpKWs6aVpB2jJYJ0ICJMm4Zld2aAnCbWv0umFfokMFOwJ725JbO8PK9qK0SDir1AETYvJw14LnlT9samyRYAbZ4UiqhF1nZ2YYgb3oNkQ-dmE4t_9WVCYumdb2IPSi-Jy5UlkK1pUOZ0AxP8bxttqXtZK8bfROA/iFLgqG2rQmtBJEJc9losdbMLaACLLSmN/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="韩国和波兰同意继续加强防务关系"&gt;进一步加强防务关系&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&g